Package: asterisk-codec-g729
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, asterisk
Description: G.729 transcoder module for Asterisk (bcg729)
 Plug-and-play G.729 <-> slin codec module for Asterisk 21/22, built on the
 Belledonne bcg729 library.
 .
 Registering the g729<->slin translators lets Asterisk transcode between G.729
 and any PCM-based codec (PCMU/PCMA/GSM/...) through its slin pivot, e.g.
 (g729@8000)->(slin@8000)->(ulaw@8000). bcg729 is linked statically, so no
 separate library package is required.
